Source: broadcom-facetimehd
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Jean Baptiste Favre <debian@jbfavre.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12), dkms
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://github.com/patjak/bcwc_pcie

Package: broadcom-facetimehd-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: firmware-broadcom-facetimehd, curl, xz-utils, cpio, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: broadcom-pcie-webcam-dkms
Description: dkms source for the Broadcom 1570 PCIe webcam
 Broadcom 1570 PCIe webcam is a device driver to support the Facetime HD
 PCIe webcam found on recent Macbooks.
 .
 This package provides the source code for factimehd kernel module and
 makes use of the DKMS build utility to install it for the running
 kernel.
 .
 Needed firmware is provided by firmware-broadcom-pcie-webcam.

Package: firmware-broadcom-facetimehd
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: firmware-broadcom-pcie-webcam
Description: Binary firmware for the Broadcom 1570 PCIe webcam
 Broadcom 1570 PCIe webcam is a device driver to support the Facetime HD
 PCIe webcam found on recent Macbooks.
 .
 This package provides the binary firmware for broadcom-pcie-webcam-dkms
 package.
